<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Arts Career Path</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stream-detail.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="stream-hero">
    <span>Creative and Humanities Stream</span>
    <h1>Arts Career Path</h1>
    <p>Arts includes humanities, design, media, language, psychology, history, political science, and creative careers. It suits students who enjoy expression, ideas, people, culture, and communication.</p>
  </header>
  <main class="stream-shell">
    <section class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Main Subjects</strong>English, History, Political Science, Psychology, Fine Arts</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Common Exams</strong>CUET, design entrance tests, university tests</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Best For</strong>Creativity, writing, research, communication</div>
    </section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Popular Arts Fields</h2>
    <section class="path-grid">
      <div class="path-card active"><h3>Media</h3><p>Journalism, content creation, public relations, advertising, and digital media.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Design</h3><p>Graphic, UI/UX, fashion, product, interior, and communication design.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Psychology</h3><p>Study behavior, emotions, learning, counselling, and human development.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Humanities</h3><p>Explore history, literature, society, politics, and public ideas.</p></div>
    </section>
    <section class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-target="courses">Courses</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="exams">Entrance Exams</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="careers">Careers</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="skills">Skills</button>
    </section>
    <section class="detail-panel">
      <div id="courses" class="tab-panel active"><h2>Courses You Can Choose</h2><ul><li>BA English, BA Psychology, BA History, BA Political Science.</li><li>BFA, Design courses, Animation, Mass Communication.</li><li>Hotel Management, Social Work, Sociology, Education paths.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="exams" class="tab-panel"><h2>Entrance Exams</h2><ul><li>CUET for many BA and humanities courses.</li><li>NID, NIFT, UCEED, or institute tests for design fields.</li><li>University-level entrance or portfolio review for creative programs.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="careers" class="tab-panel"><h2>Career Options</h2><ul><li>Journalist, Designer, Writer, Content Creator, Animator.</li><li>Psychologist after higher studies, Teacher, Researcher, Social Worker.</li><li>Civil Services, Public Policy, PR, Advertising, Editor.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="skills" class="tab-panel"><h2>Skills To Build</h2><ul><li>Writing, speaking, research, observation, and creative thinking.</li><li>Portfolio building for design, media, and art careers.</li><li>Critical thinking and understanding society.</li></ul></div>
    </section>
    <section class="planner"><h2>Student Checklist</h2><label><input type="checkbox"> Build a writing, design, or media portfolio.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Compare BA subjects before choosing one.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Practice reading and presentation skills.</label></section>
    <div class="back-row"><a class="action-link" href="career.jsp">Back to Career Streams</a></div>
  </main>
  <script src="stream-detail.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
